June Elvidge https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/June_Elvidge 0 June Elvidge (June 30, 1893 – May 1, 1965) was an early 20th-century silent film actress from St. Paul, Minnesota. She was of English and Irish descent. June_Elvidge ( June_30_,_1893 – May_1_,_1965 ) was an_early_20th-century_silent_film_actress from St._Paul , Minnesota . She was of English_and_Irish_descent .
